headline: Jefferies Cuts Lululemon Athletica Inc. (LULU) Price Target Even as Wall Street Expects Sales Growth
summary: Lululemon Athletica Inc. (NASDAQ:LULU) is one of the top stocks in Michael Burry’s stock portfolio. On October 6, an analyst at Jefferies reiterated an ‘Underperform’ rating on the stock and cut the price target to $120 from $150.
